short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Download the current tab in Google Sheets as PDF or XLSX with one click. Created by Prashant Mishra, helping thousands of users.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Now it is easy to download the current tab in Google Sheets as XLSX or PDF. If you use the default option available from the File > Download option in Google Sheets, you get the entire sheet with all the tabs included, but sometimes to share a specific tab with your colleagues, this extension will come in handy. Created by Prashant Mishra as part of his pet project, this extension has now helped thousands of users.

If you're liking the extension, please make sure rate it so it can reach more people. Thank you.
